Gene Kelly

This is a photo of Gene Kelly added by Amanda S. Stevenson on August 6, 2020. Juan Pablo de la Cruz, a circus expert in Campeche, Mexico had this caption: Speaking of Gene and the circus, here he is as an aerialist in Thousands Cheer (1943). He told me that he did all of his own stunts except for the double somersault on the trapeze without a net. “I can’t do that,” he said.
